<li id="cite_note-17"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17" title="">^</a></b> <a href="http://www.truecrypt.org/docs/supported-operating-systems.php" class="external text" title="http://www.truecrypt.org/docs/supported-operating-systems.php" rel="nofollow">TrueCrypt - Free Open-Source Disk Encryption Software - Documentation - Supported Operating Systems</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
<p><a name="External_links" id="External_links"></a></p>
